name: NormalDeliveryAndOtherIndicationsForCare
title: Normal Delivery and Other Indications for Care
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains diagnoses that represent  normal delivery and other indications for care for which delivery is referenced.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify normal delivery and other indications for care for which delivery is referenced. Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the "Diagnosis" category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include ICD 9 CM codes that identify normal delivery and other indications for care for which delivery is referenced.),(Exclusion Criteria: Exclude codes that do not meet the inclusion criteria.)
